author: pburba
msg: On the 1.6.x-issue3654 branch: Adjust a merge test's expectations.
(merge_to_target_with_copied_children): This is the one test in the 1.6.x
suite that actually expected a merge to not update subtree mergeinfo.
all subtrees get updated with mergeinfo to describe the merge.

author: jeremias
msg: Moved all Java2D- and Color-related classes to org.apache.xmlgraphics.java2d.color in order to avoid clutter in the parent package.
Deprecated CMYKColorSpace which was already in the previous release.
